sp.p:
Yes madam. And you can't think how they act;
some are jumping up for joy — some are laughing, and some
are almost crying, they are so pleased.

Sir, you are very welcome here, and most cordially will we entertain you;
(hands a chair,)
sit down sir, and it will not be long, before we shall have some refreshment ready for you.

My friends, if you will tarry awhile with us, we
will endeavour to enlighten you in the christian religion;
we feel for you, and greatly desire your salvation.
